{"id": "48860", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=48860", "title": "Tongue Rippers", "text": "The Tongue Rippers (a.k.a. Rippers) are an order of executioners that serve the &lt;a href=\"Cathedral%20of%20Light\"&gt;Cathedral of Light&lt;/a&gt;. Stoic, merciless, and unaffected by their own emotions and opinions, these imposing figures are a reminder of what happens if one strays from the flock. They carry the tongues of those who've fallen beneath their blades. They must not take pleasure in their holy work, for to do so invites a fall."}
