 href=\"monsters\"&gt;monsters&lt;/a&gt; in the game.\nBonuses:\nDevelopment.\nIn beta SuperUniques.txt Toorc has 3 minions.\nToorc Icefist has an unused turquoise color palette due to Council Member monsters lack of palshift.dat file."}
