{"id": "5663", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5663", "title": "Totemic Mask", "text": "Totemic Masks are the &lt;a href=\"Exceptional%20Items\"&gt;exceptional&lt;/a&gt; versions of &lt;a href=\"Spirit%20Mask\"&gt;Spirit Mask&lt;/a&gt;s. They are usable only by &lt;a href=\"Druid\"&gt;Druid&lt;/a&gt;s.\nThe Totemic Mask resembles an &lt;a href=\"Alpha%20Helm\"&gt;Alpha Helm&lt;/a&gt; but with certain spiritual markings and a characteristic red glow in the Wolf's eyes. These may just be rubies embedded into the totem to enhance its spiritual power. \nLike all other &lt;a href=\"Druid%20Pelts\"&gt;Druid Pelts&lt;/a&gt;, the Totemic Mask helps the Druid commune with the spirits of nature. But to a lesser extent than the Elite Pelts, which are the direct totems of the Spirits themselves.\nDruid Pelts can have 1-3 bonuses of +1-3 to specific &lt;a href=\"Druid%23Skills\"&gt;Druid Skills&lt;/a&gt;."}
