{"id": "53331", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=53331", "title": "Touch of Death", "text": "Touch of Death is an &lt;a href=\"event%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;event&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Act%20V%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act V&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It takes place in an open plaza in the &lt;a href=\"Westmarch%20Commons\"&gt;Westmarch Commons&lt;/a&gt;.\nA few cots with wounded guards are set up around the square in the plaza, with a lone Westmarch Guard still standing, but in despair. &lt;a href=\"The%20Nephalem\"&gt;The Nephalem&lt;/a&gt; must assist him in stopping a wave of attacking &lt;a href=\"Punisher\"&gt;Punisher&lt;/a&gt;s, but he is killed nonetheless when a &lt;a href=\"Death%20Maiden\"&gt;Death Maiden&lt;/a&gt; emerges from the ground and brings with her &lt;a href=\"Revenant%20Soldier\"&gt;Revenant Soldier&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Summoned%20Archer\"&gt;Summoned Archer&lt;/a&gt;s, and &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20of%20Death\"&gt;Shadows of Death&lt;/a&gt;. Defeating this group completes the event.\nObjectives.\nKilling just the first couple Punishers accomplishes the corresponding objective, but clearing the remainder completes the objective to talk to the guard."}
