{"id": "46526", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=46526", "title": "Tovri", "text": "Tovri was a resident of &lt;a href=\"Nevesk\"&gt;Nevesk&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231336\"&gt;1336&lt;/a&gt;, Nevesk came under the sway of &lt;a href=\"Lilith\"&gt;Lilith&lt;/a&gt;.\nWhen arrived in the &lt;a href=\"town\"&gt;town&lt;/a&gt;, they were directed to &lt;a href=\"Icehowl%20Ruins\"&gt;Icehowl Ruins&lt;/a&gt;. The Wanderer investigated the ruins and survived, much to the surprise of the villagers, Tovri included. They posed a celebration in order to drug the Wanderer. They succeeded, but the Wanderer escaped with the aid of &lt;a href=\"Iosef\"&gt;Iosef&lt;/a&gt;. Tovri and the other villagers attacked them, but were killed in the fight.\nIn-game.\nTovri is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\". He is first introduced in the tavern in &lt;a href=\"Nevesk\"&gt;Nevesk&lt;/a&gt;, as part of the \"&lt;a href=\"Dusk%20on%20the%20Mountain\"&gt;Dusk on the Mountain&lt;/a&gt;\" &lt;a href=\"quest\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt;. During &lt;a href=\"A%20Hero%27s%20Reward\"&gt;A Hero's Reward&lt;/a&gt;, he becomes a &lt;a href=\"Monster\"&gt;Monster&lt;/a&gt;. As a monster, he uses a &lt;a href=\"maces\"&gt;mace&lt;/a&gt;.\nQuotes.\nDuring &lt;a href=\"Dusk%20on%20the%20Mountain\"&gt;Dusk on the Mountain&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"A%20Hero%27s%20Return\"&gt;A Hero's Return&lt;/a&gt;, before speaking to &lt;a href=\"Vani\"&gt;Vani&lt;/a&gt;. He can be found behind the bar in the tavern."}
