{"id": "31616", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=31616", "title": "Treason's Final Reward", "text": "Treason's Final Reward is an found in the &lt;a href=\"Paths%20of%20the%20Drowned\"&gt;Paths of the Drowned&lt;/a&gt; in of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nIn their journeys, &lt;a href=\"the%20Nephalem\"&gt;the Nephalem&lt;/a&gt; may encounter a pit with the Pillar of the Faithless in its center. Touching the pillar will unleash a swarm of &lt;a href=\"Skeleton\"&gt;Skeleton&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"Skeletal%20Archer\"&gt;Skeletal Archer&lt;/a&gt;s led by &lt;a href=\"Magnar\"&gt;Magnar&lt;/a&gt;. Killing them all ends the event, rewarding &lt;a href=\"experience\"&gt;experience&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"gold\"&gt;gold&lt;/a&gt;.\nApparently, the pillar served as a prison of sorts for the &lt;a href=\"soul\"&gt;soul&lt;/a&gt;s of those who betrayed &lt;a href=\"Rakkis\"&gt;Rakkis&lt;/a&gt;."}
