{"id": "25542", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=25542", "title": "Hellfire Ring (other)", "text": "The Hellfire Ring is a &lt;a href=\"Craftable%20items\"&gt;craftable&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"rings\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 1 to be used, but its affixes roll as high as those of level 70 items. It also has seven affixes as opposed to usual six.\nThe ring, unlike its other variations, is a reward for players who do the &lt;a href=\"Infernal%20Machine\"&gt;Infernal Machine&lt;/a&gt; event at the level cap of 70. As such, this ring variation requires access to \"&lt;a href=\"Reaper%20of%20Souls\"&gt;Reaper of Souls&lt;/a&gt;.\"\nNote that while Hellfire Rings come in five variations, they are all called simply \"&lt;a href=\"Hellfire%20Ring\"&gt;Hellfire Ring&lt;/a&gt;\".\nThe unique affix creates a 20 yard radius area of molten lava dealing 200% damage as &lt;a href=\"Fire\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; per second for 6 seconds. The area is created at the location of the character, not at the location of the target. Multiple applications from the same character do not stack.\nCrafting.\nThe Hellfire Ring can be crafted using the Design: Hellfire Ring, 50,000 gold, 1 &lt;a href=\"Leoric%27s%20Regret\"&gt;Leoric's Regret&lt;/a&gt;, 1 &lt;a href=\"Vial%20of%20Putridness\"&gt;Vial of Putridness&lt;/a&gt;, 1 &lt;a href=\"Idol%20of%20Terror\"&gt;Idol of Terror&lt;/a&gt;, and 1 &lt;a href=\"Heart%20of%20Evil\"&gt;Heart of Evil&lt;/a&gt;."}
