{"id": "6792", "revid": "21257", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6792", "title": "Hellplague", "text": "Hellplague is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; from .\nUseful on multiple facets, Hellplague is a fascinating sword. On the physical end, Hellplague's strength lies in its elemental damage. Although its damage without bonuses may seem lackluster (with a particularly low minimum damage), Hellplague bestows a very high amount of &lt;a href=\"Fire\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; damage, as well as &lt;a href=\"Poison\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt; damage. Although certainly not as effective against enemies immune to either Fire, Poison, or both, Hellplague can still do a good amount of damage against those who aren't.\nHellplague also bestows both &lt;a href=\"life\"&gt;life&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"mana\"&gt;mana&lt;/a&gt; leech. Physical fighters such as s or &lt;a href=\"Amazon\"&gt;Amazon&lt;/a&gt;s, who use mana-consuming skills, but often don't typically invest in &lt;a href=\"Energy\"&gt;Energy&lt;/a&gt;, would especially find mana leech useful.\nHowever, most interesting is Hellplague's bonuses to &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Skills\"&gt;Fire Skills&lt;/a&gt;. Besides a &lt;a href=\"Sorceress\"&gt;Sorceress&lt;/a&gt;' &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Spells\"&gt;Fire Spells&lt;/a&gt; or a &lt;a href=\"Druid\"&gt;Druid&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"Elemental%20Skills\"&gt;Elemental Skills&lt;/a&gt;, not many characters have a wide variety of fire skills. However, the &lt;a href=\"Paladin\"&gt;Paladin&lt;/a&gt; does have &lt;a href=\"Holy%20Fire\"&gt;Holy Fire&lt;/a&gt;, and considering that they are most likely to use either swords or &lt;a href=\"Maces\"&gt;Maces&lt;/a&gt;, Hellplague may be better off in the hands of a Paladin.\nAnother possible use is in combination with &lt;a href=\"Enchant\"&gt;Enchant&lt;/a&gt;. Since Hellplague does decent damage and would give a boost to Enchant, it could be used by Sorceresses to have a more effective Enchant.\nStats.\nOne-Hand Damage: 5 To (32-34)\nRequired Level: 22\nRequired Strength: 55\nRequired Dexterity: 39\nDurability: 44\nSword Class - "}
