{"id": "19483", "revid": "9305822", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19483", "title": "Hidden Camp", "text": "Hidden Camp is a location in &lt;a href=\"Act%20II%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act II&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\nThe camp was set up on a bluff overlooking &lt;a href=\"Caldeum\"&gt;Caldeum&lt;/a&gt;. The site was chosen by &lt;a href=\"Tyrael\"&gt;Tyrael&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Leah\"&gt;Leah&lt;/a&gt;, who wanted to keep the camp's location secret.\nIn-game.\nThe camp serves as the main \"&lt;a href=\"Towns\"&gt;town&lt;/a&gt;\" in the act (main evidence being, when using &lt;a href=\"Town%20Portal\"&gt;Town Portal&lt;/a&gt;, player(s) is/are transported here).\nFrom the camp, the player can go &lt;a href=\"Caldeum%20Bazaar\"&gt;Caldeum Bazaar&lt;/a&gt; and through it to &lt;a href=\"Sundered%20Canyon\"&gt;Sundered Canyon&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Flooded%20Causeway\"&gt;Flooded Causeway&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Palace%20Gates\"&gt;Palace Gates&lt;/a&gt;."}
