{"id": "44416", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=44416", "title": "Hidden Sun", "text": "Hidden Sun is a &lt;a href=\"cosmetic%20set\"&gt;cosmetic set&lt;/a&gt; released in &lt;a href=\"Season%20%28Diablo%20Immortal%29\"&gt;Season 8&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". \nThematically, it appears to tie in with the &lt;a href=\"Exalted%20Night\"&gt;Exalted Night&lt;/a&gt; event and/or the associated lore of the &lt;a href=\"Voidwound%20Cage\"&gt;Voidwound Cage&lt;/a&gt;. The aesthetic of this set is themed around an &lt;a href=\"https%3A//en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eclipse\"&gt;eclipse&lt;/a&gt;."}
