{"id": "19460", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19460", "title": "Highlands Crossing", "text": "The Highlands Crossing is an area connecting the &lt;a href=\"Caverns%20of%20Araneae\"&gt;Caverns of Araneae&lt;/a&gt; to the &lt;a href=\"Southern%20Highlands\"&gt;Southern Highlands&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Act%20I%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act I&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It consists of a small plateau connected by a bridge to the northwest to the main Highlands area. A river flows northward under the bridge, then falls down the cliffs to the farmland below.\n&lt;a href=\"Karyna\"&gt;Karyna&lt;/a&gt; stays at the Crossing after being rescued from &lt;a href=\"Queen%20Araneae\"&gt;Queen Araneae&lt;/a&gt; and explaining her theft of the Khazra staff for the &lt;a href=\"Trailing%20the%20Coven\"&gt;Trailing the Coven&lt;/a&gt; quest.\nApart from hidden Withermoths which emerge from the bushes if one gets too close, the area may be completely empty of monsters. Occasionally a few can be found, especially in the form of an &lt;a href=\"Elite%20pack\"&gt;Elite pack&lt;/a&gt;. A &lt;a href=\"Khazra%20Shaman\"&gt;Khazra Shaman&lt;/a&gt; stands at the end of the bridge just before crossing into the Southern Highlands proper.\nHighlands Crossing is a distinct zone only in &lt;a href=\"Campaign%20Mode\"&gt;Campaign Mode&lt;/a&gt;. In &lt;a href=\"Adventure%20Mode\"&gt;Adventure Mode&lt;/a&gt;, it is simply part of the Southern Highlands, and the &lt;a href=\"waypoint\"&gt;waypoint&lt;/a&gt; located there is labeled accordingly."}
