{"id": "4779", "revid": "1032478", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4779", "title": "Raven Frost", "text": "Raven Frost is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Rings\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt; from \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nPerhaps a cold version of fellow unique ring, &lt;a href=\"Dwarf%20Star\"&gt;Dwarf Star&lt;/a&gt;, Raven Frost can help build up a very good defense against Cold attacks, especially when combined with equipment such as &lt;a href=\"Hawkmail\"&gt;Hawkmail&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Medusa%27s%20Gaze\"&gt;Medusa's Gaze&lt;/a&gt;. Physical fighters may value it for its attack rating bonuses as well as the &lt;a href=\"Cannot%20Be%20Frozen\"&gt;Cannot Be Frozen&lt;/a&gt; property. Spellcasters may appreciate its bonus to &lt;a href=\"Mana\"&gt;Mana&lt;/a&gt;, and possibly dexterity for added block.\nStats.\nRequired Level: 45"}
{"id": "6328", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6328", "title": "Ravenlore", "text": "The Ravenlore is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Sky%20Spirit\"&gt;Sky Spirit&lt;/a&gt; found in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\". It can only be equipped by &lt;a href=\"Druid\"&gt;Druid&lt;/a&gt;s. \nBesides its substantial boost to &lt;a href=\"Raven\"&gt;Raven&lt;/a&gt;, Ravenlore is also the only unique &lt;a href=\"Druid%20Pelts\"&gt;pelt&lt;/a&gt; that gives bonuses to &lt;a href=\"Elemental%20Skills\"&gt;Elemental Skills&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Energy\"&gt;Energy&lt;/a&gt;, not to mention a reduction of enemy &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Resist\"&gt;Fire Resist&lt;/a&gt;. Ravenlore is more useful for Druid builds centered around Elemental Skills, particularly &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Skills\"&gt;Fire Skills&lt;/a&gt; such as the &lt;a href=\"Volcano\"&gt;Volcano&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Armageddon\"&gt;Armageddon&lt;/a&gt;.\nStats.\nDefense: \nRequired Level: 74\nRequired Strength: 113\nDurability: 20"}
{"id": "39097", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=39097", "title": "Ravenous Bite", "text": "Ravenous Bite\u00a0is a Defensive Shapeshift skill used by\u00a0\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\", inspired by &lt;a href=\"Hunger\"&gt;Hunger&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn-game.\nHealing provided by this skill does not depend on the actual amount of damage done, and instead heals a fixed amount as long as a damaging hit is scored. The amount of healing is higher than the potential damage.\nWhen cast, the Druid immediately shifts into the Werewolf form, and the skill itself always counts as being cast in it. Lasts for 3 seconds or until a non-Werewolf skill is cast."}
