{"id": "46037", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=46037", "title": "Razed Village", "text": "The is a destroyed village located in the south-western region of the &lt;a href=\"Foggy%20Plains\"&gt;Foggy Plains&lt;/a&gt;.\nLore.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Anno%20Kehjistani%23Damhar\"&gt;Damhar&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;1270&lt;/a&gt;, the village was attacked by a large force of &lt;a href=\"khazra\"&gt;khazra&lt;/a&gt;. Help was sent by &lt;a href=\"Sentinel%27s%20Watch\"&gt;Sentinel's Watch&lt;/a&gt;, but the soldiers were defeated. &lt;a href=\"Lieutenant%20Ralvar\"&gt;One soldier&lt;/a&gt; managed to escape to warn &lt;a href=\"Captain%20Vereks\"&gt;Captain Vereks&lt;/a&gt;. He returned with an &lt;a href=\"the%20Shard-seeker\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt; who volunteered to help. Together they were able to drive back the khazra.\nThe village remains in ruins, as the villagers not killed by the khazra were sacrificed in order to summon &lt;a href=\"Blood%20Clan\"&gt;Blood Clan&lt;/a&gt; khazra as reinforcement. The restless ghosts of some of the dead villagers haunt the village. Though they were initially driven off, the ruins of the village was later reoccupied by khazra.\nIn-game.\nThe is a &lt;a href=\"Mount%20Zavain\"&gt;Mount Zavain&lt;/a&gt; zone in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". It is first encountered in the &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal%20quests\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt;, \"&lt;a href=\"Free%20the%20Captives\"&gt;Free the Captives&lt;/a&gt;.\""}
