{"id": "38823", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=38823", "title": "Rend (Diablo IV)", "text": "Rend\u00a0is a Fury skill used by\u00a0\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\".\nIn-game.\nUnlike the classic &lt;a href=\"Rend\"&gt;Rend&lt;/a&gt;, hits a cone in front of the player instead of the circular area, applying both instant damage and &lt;a href=\"Bleed\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt;. The Bleed effect does not stack (only refreshes to full duration), but is separate from the Bleeding of &lt;a href=\"Flay\"&gt;Flay&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Blood%20Thirst\"&gt;Blood Thirst&lt;/a&gt; and other skills.\nRemember that Bleed effects cannot roll &lt;a href=\"Critical%20Hit\"&gt;Critical Hit&lt;/a&gt;s, but instead are increased in damage proportionally to the Critical Hit Chance/Damage ratio.\nRequires a slashing weapon (&lt;a href=\"Swords\"&gt;Swords&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Axes\"&gt;Axes&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Two-Handed%20Swords\"&gt;Two-Handed Swords&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Two-Handed%20Axes\"&gt;Two-Handed Axes&lt;/a&gt;) to be equipped and switches to those when used.\nCounts as Berserker skill."}
