{"id": "49500", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49500", "title": "Karamat's Reach", "text": "Karamat's Reach was a &lt;a href=\"Malignant%20Tunnel\"&gt;Malignant Tunnel&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\", exclusive to \"&lt;a href=\"Season%20of%20the%20Malignant\"&gt;Season of the Malignant&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\nKaramat's Reach was a &lt;a href=\"Zakarum\"&gt;Zakarum&lt;/a&gt; outpost in &lt;a href=\"Hawezar\"&gt;Hawezar&lt;/a&gt;, though according to &lt;a href=\"Cormond\"&gt;Cormond&lt;/a&gt;, the outpost was a pre-existing structure appropriated by Zakarum rather than built by the church itself. It was a base of operations for the &lt;a href=\"Zakarum%20Inquisition\"&gt;Zakarum Inquisition&lt;/a&gt;, which conducted experiments with &lt;a href=\"Cages%20of%20Binding\"&gt;Cages of Binding&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Malignant\"&gt;Malignant&lt;/a&gt;/Malignant-like creatures. Those present reported to &lt;a href=\"Orbei%20Monastery\"&gt;Orbei Monastery&lt;/a&gt;. The experiments progressed to the point where they could extract &lt;a href=\"Malignant%20Heart\"&gt;Malignant Heart&lt;/a&gt;s, but as before, it always resulted in the subject's &lt;a href=\"death\"&gt;death&lt;/a&gt;. The experiments apparently had a theological bent to them as well, as they sought to remove \"the darkness from the &lt;a href=\"light\"&gt;light&lt;/a&gt;.\" After 112 days of experiments, the inquisitors created a perfect cage that simply killed the subject, and in so doing, spare them from the fate of malignancy.\nKaramat's Reach was buried and forgotten, the only means of entry being the conduction of a ritual. For a century, no one tried to explore the outpost, not even the &lt;a href=\"Crusaders\"&gt;Crusaders&lt;/a&gt;. However, in &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231336\"&gt;1336&lt;/a&gt;, Cormond and entered the outpost, where they found the &lt;a href=\"soul\"&gt;spirits&lt;/a&gt; of the dead within the outpost, along with an advanced Cage of Binding they could use to kill &lt;a href=\"Varshan\"&gt;Varshan&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn-game.\nKaramat's Reach was explored in the \"&lt;a href=\"Ruins%20of%20the%20Faith\"&gt;Ruins of the Faith&lt;/a&gt;\" quest.\nPoints of Interest.\nWithin the outpost, old Inquisition logs could be found:"}
