{"id": "42238", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=42238", "title": "Keeper", "text": "The Keeper is a type of &lt;a href=\"undead\"&gt;undead&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"monster\"&gt;monster&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". \nLore.\nNot all who stalk the swirling sands of Zoltun Kulle's library are creations of the mad &lt;a href=\"mage\"&gt;mage&lt;/a&gt;. The ambient &lt;a href=\"magic\"&gt;magic&lt;/a&gt; of the library seems to have a lingering instinct; it twists, animates, and binds the &lt;a href=\"soul\"&gt;soul&lt;/a&gt;s of the dead to servitude, all in defense of keeping an abandoned machine creaking along for centuries.\nIn life, the Keepers were &lt;a href=\"Horadrim\"&gt;Horadrim&lt;/a&gt;, sent to invade the &lt;a href=\"Library%20of%20Zoltun%20Kulle\"&gt;Library of Zoltun Kulle&lt;/a&gt;. However, &lt;a href=\"Zoltun%20Kulle\"&gt;Kulle&lt;/a&gt; defeated them. Their souls were bound in servitude by the library, which resurrected them as &lt;a href=\"undead\"&gt;undead&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn-game.\nKeepers are found in the &lt;a href=\"Hidden%20Alcove\"&gt;Hidden Alcove&lt;/a&gt; in the Library of Zoltun Kulle."}
