{"id": "48079", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=48079", "title": "Keepers", "text": "The Keepers are a watcher order based in &lt;a href=\"T%C3%BAr%20D%C3%BAlra\"&gt;T\u00far D\u00falra&lt;/a&gt;. They stand in eternal watch over &lt;a href=\"Gl%C3%B3r-an-Fh%C3%A1idha\"&gt;Gl\u00f3r-an-Fh\u00e1idha&lt;/a&gt;. They wear wooden armor, which stands as a symbol of their protection over the great tree and all nature. They carry &lt;a href=\"staves\"&gt;staves&lt;/a&gt; taken from the branches of the Great Oak itself, and the words of the &lt;a href=\"Sc%C3%A9al%20Fada\"&gt;Sc\u00e9al Fada&lt;/a&gt; are etched upon their hearts."}
