{"id": "46673", "revid": "51979909", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=46673", "title": "Khaliun", "text": "Biography.\nKhaliun was a woman that was corrupted by a demonic cleaver. She was known for the number of lovers she had, each disappearing after the next. Her story is told during the quest &lt;a href=\"In%20the%20Name%20of%20Love\"&gt;In the Name of Love&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Dry%20Steppes\"&gt;Dry Steppes&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "34424", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=34424", "title": "Khamhalla", "text": "Khamhalla is a ruined city. Long ago, it was ruled by a wise &lt;a href=\"nephalem\"&gt;nephalem&lt;/a&gt; king. The king was wounded during the city's fall, but he did not die. Instead, he was borne away across the sea, to return when &lt;a href=\"Sanctuary\"&gt;Sanctuary&lt;/a&gt; needed him again."}
